text.section:
This section applies to:
The Faculty;
A component medical society of the Faculty;
A committee of the Faculty or of a component medical society of the Faculty;
A committee appointed by or established in the Maryland Institute for Emergency Medical Services Systems;
A hospital, related institution, or other health care facility staff committee;
A hospital, related institution, or other health care facility credentials committee or its equivalent;
The chief executive officer of a hospital, related institution, or other health care facility;
The dean of any medical school in this State;
A member of the Board;
A casualty insurer writing medical professional liability insurance in this State;
A utilization committee of:
A nonprofit health service plan; or
A health insurer doing business in this State;
The chief executive officer of an alternative health system;
The medical director of an alternative health system;
A medical review committee appointed by or established in an alternative health system; and
A physician.
